<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10122105>
    dc:description "FIGURES 14–22. Terminalia of Neohybos colombiensis, sp. n. 14–18, male: 14, epandrium and cerci, dorsal view; 15, epandrium, ventral view (apex of hypandrium outlined); 16, 17, left and right epandrial lamellae, lateral view; 18, hypandrium, ventral view. 19–22, female: dorsal, right lateral, left lateral and ventral views. Figs 14–18; 19–22 in the same scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10122105/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10122125>
    dc:description "FIGURES 74–81. Wings of Neohybos: 74, N. bicolor sp. n.; 75, N. brunnescens sp. n.; 76, N. colombiensis sp. n.; 77, N. cooperi sp. n.; 78, N. cupreus sp. n.; 79, N. elegans sp. n.; 80, N. fuscipes sp. n.; 81, N. tenuis sp. n." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10122125/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

